-da-ngay-fine-repair-veil', '', '', '1970-01-01 08:00:00', '1970-01-01 08:00:00', '', 0, 'https://hkshop.vn/duong-da-ngay-fine-repair-veil-p10785.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
